- Administrative Expenses (most frequent): adding all including entries like 22627.45, 46979.81, 91203.96, etc.
- Sales Expenses: sum of entries like 74676.94, 23656.57, 29738.59, etc.
- Financial Expenses: sum of entries like 92015.1, 58288.72, etc.
- Depreciation: including entries such as 45745.8, 45751.41, etc.
